  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d03bc636d4f22964e964f316abda6d60, type: 3}
  m_Name: Story 3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  chapter: 3
  title: Racing With Newton
  story: "You enter a neon hover arena above ruined city towers, your upgraded racer
    humming beneath you. Competitors surround you, ready to collide and test your
    skill. Gizmo warns that this race is all about mastering forces.\n\nThe moment
    the race starts, inertia slams you sideways on the first curve. You counter with
    quick thruster control, remembering Newton\u2019s laws to keep the hover stable.\n\nOpponents
    bump and push, trying to throw you off the track. You predict how each hit affects
    your motion, using action-reaction forces to stay balanced and ahead.\n\nIn the
    final sprint, two racers trap you, but you time a perfect boost. You slip through
    and cross the finish line first, earning the prize money for your next major
    upgrades."
